This paper deals with the topic of internet censorship, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves web crawling techniques and network analysis, which are relevant to the sub-categories of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), digital libraries (cs.DL), social and information networks (cs.SI), and cryptography and security (cs.CY).
